### Genfeed API - Personas Content Endpoints
### AI persona content generation: photos, videos, voice, captions, content plans
### Protected by RolesGuard

########################################
# Content Generation
########################################

### Generate Persona Photo
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/{{testPersonaId}}/generate/photo
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Professional headshot in a modern office setting"
}


### Generate Persona Video
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/{{testPersonaId}}/generate/video
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "script": "Hi everyone! Today I want to share three tips for growing your audience using AI-generated content.",
  "aspectRatio": "9:16"
}


### Generate Persona Voice
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/{{testPersonaId}}/generate/voice
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Welcome to our weekly content strategy breakdown. Let me walk you through the key insights.",
  "ingredientId": "{{testIngredientId}}"
}


### Generate Persona Caption
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/{{testPersonaId}}/generate/caption
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "AI content creation trends",
  "platform": "instagram"
}


########################################
# Content Planning & Publishing
########################################

### Generate Content Plan
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/{{testPersonaId}}/content-plan
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "days": 7,
  "credentialId": "{{testCredentialId}}"
}


### Generate Content Plan (Preview Only)
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/{{testPersonaId}}/content-plan
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "days": 14
}


### Publish Persona Content
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/{{testPersonaId}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "The future of AI in content creation is here. Three things every marketer needs to know...",
  "ingredientIds": ["{{testIngredientId}}"],
  "category": "image",
  "scheduledDate": "2026-02-20T10:00:00.000Z"
}


########################################
# Persona Posts
########################################

### Get Persona Posts
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/{{testPersonaId}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Persona Posts with Pagination
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/{{testPersonaId}}/posts?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Test Cases
########################################

### Test: Generate Photo for Non-Existent Persona
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/generate/photo
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "test photo"
}


### Test: Generate Video Without Script
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/{{testPersonaId}}/generate/video
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}


### Test: Unauthorized Access
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/personas/{{testPersonaId}}/posts
